          </statement>

          <feedback>
            <p>Can you have 2.5 people in a household?</p>
          </feedback>
        </choice>

        <choice>
          <statement>
            <p>boolean</p>
          </statement>

          <feedback>
            <p>Is the number of people something that is either true or false?</p>
          </feedback>
        </choice>

        <choice>
          <statement>
            <p>String</p>
          </statement>

          <feedback>
            <p>
              While you can use a string, a number is better for doing
